snippet.title: ZombieGirl (All Endings + All Secrets) [HD]
snippet.description:
Player:Chiara
ZombieGirl-Zombie growing game 
All Endings & All Secrets

[[Info]]
Game: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.karapon.zombieGirlForeign

Zombiegirl is a mobile game where you have found yourself in a world with zombies.
There are total of 14 different zombies, 3 endings and 11 secrets.
